Package: Rmlx
Type: Package
Title: R Interface to MLX Arrays (GPU-Accelerated with Metal or CUDA)
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: c(
    person("David", "Hugh-Jones", email = "david@hughjones.com", role = c("aut", "cre")),
    person("Apple Inc.", role = c("cph"), comment = "MLX library (bundled in src/mlx-src)")
    )
Author: David Hugh-Jones [aut, cre],
    Apple Inc. [cph] (MLX library bundled in src/mlx-src)
Maintainer: David Hugh-Jones <david@hughjones.com>
Description: S3 class 'mlx' backed by MLX arrays with lazy GPU ops via Rcpp. Supports Metal backend on macOS (Apple Silicon) and CUDA backend on Linux (Nvidia GPUs).
