    ggplot2
VignetteBuilder: knitr
Config/testthat/edition: 3
SystemRequirements: C++17, CMake (>= 3.24); macOS on Apple Silicon (M1 or later) for Metal backend; Linux with NVIDIA GPU and CUDA toolkit (>= 12.0) for CUDA backend
